1. Moja sestra je zaposlena u *radnji* (My sister is employed at a *shop*).
2. Ova *radnja* prodaje odeću za decu (This *store* sells children's clothing).
3. On je vlasnik ove *radnje* (He is the owner of this *shop*).
4. Danas sam kupila knjigu u *radnji* (Today I bought a book at the *store*).
5. Molim te, idi u *radnju* i kupi mleko (Please go to the *shop* and buy some milk).
6. Oni su zatvorili svoju *radnju* zbog pandemije (They closed their *business* due to the pandemic).
7. Ova *radnja* nudi različite vrste čokolade (This *shop* offers different types of chocolate).
8. Ja bih volela da otvorim svoju *radnju* jednog dana (I would like to open my own *store* one day).
9. Prodavačica u *radnji* je bila vrlo ljubazna prema meni (The saleswoman at the *shop* was very kind to me).
10. Kada sam bila dete, volela sam da idem u *radnju* sa svojom bakom (When I was a child, I loved going to the *store* with my grandma).